flowchart TD
    Start([开始]) --> SelectMethod{选择矿种输入方式}
    
    SelectMethod --> |标准列表| StdList[Minerals Scope 页面选择]
    SelectMethod --> |自定义| CustomInput[手动输入矿种名称]
    
    StdList --> Check7[选择最多7种标准矿产]
    Check7 --> FillDecl[继续填写 Declaration]
    
    CustomInput --> EnterName[输入矿种名称]
    EnterName --> EnterAlias[输入别名 可选]
    EnterAlias --> AddMore{添加更多?}
    
    AddMore --> |是| EnterName
    AddMore --> |否| CheckCount{至少1种?}
    
    CheckCount --> |是| FillDecl
    CheckCount --> |否| ErrorMsg[错误: 至少选择1种矿产]
    ErrorMsg --> SelectMethod
    
    style SelectMethod fill:#fce4ec,stroke:#c2185b
    style StdList fill:#e8f5e9,stroke:#388e3c
    style CustomInput fill:#e3f2fd,stroke:#1976d2
